    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww2.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7487"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Major Talent Inc. presents AbbaMania with Night Fever and guest"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>ABBAMANIA Canada, is back at the Georgian Theatre Barrie, Friday November 27 with Night Fever as the Bee Gees plus special guest tribute to Freddie Mercury.</p>\n\n<p>The show consists of studio musicians, live strings plus an incredible front 4 that recreate Abba ... live in concert. The musicianship, vocals, costumes and choreography are unparalleled anywhere. Hear all the hits from Waterloo, Take a Chance, S.O.S, Super Trooper to Dancing Queen.</p>\n\n<p>Also on the show is Night Fever, the ultimate tribute to The Bee Gees. With all the high harmonies and stage presence the Bee Gees were known for, the concert experience is recreated  with your favorites from a catalogue spanning 5 decades including Jive Talking, To Love Somebody, I started a Joke, Stayin' Alive , You Should Be Dancing' plus many more.</p>\n\n<p>Abbamania and Night Fever have been touring for the last 20 years and will take you back in time when Abba and The Bee Gees ruled the pop music world.  Special guest for this show is Sean Hauk projecting the live illusion of the incredible Freddie Mercury.   </p>\n\n<p>It's an amazing show; it's a whole lot of fun and You're Gonna Love It!</p>\n\n\n\n\n"
      }
