      {
        "@value": "<p>50th Anniversary Alberta Zirka Ukrainian Performers - Year End Concert and Alumni Performance. Join us in celebrating of our 50th Anniversary on April 25 at 1:00pm.  </p> \n    \n<p><i>*Babies in Arms require a ticket for admission into the theatre\n<br>\n**Patrons with mobility issues and wheelchairs, are asked to please contact the Maclab Box Office at 780-980-7170 for Floor Seating (seating is limited)</i></p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>\n\n    "
