    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Bruce County Bash"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>The Bruce County Bash is back in Saugeen Shores this Canada Day long weekend! Featuring award winning artists APRIL WINE featuring Dwayne Gretzky w/ local opener Grey Road One! Come support the annual Hospital Foundation fundraiser and enjoy the best live music the area has to offer. Tickets are very limited due to the small venue space, so grab your tickets NOW!</p>\n\n<p><b>GA 19+: </b><i>Includes area on floor and in stands.</i><br><br>\n<b>VIP 19+:</b> <i>Includes early entry 5:00 p.m. / line skip into the venue / autograph session with bands before the event 5:30-6:00 p.m. (if you so choose) / first access to exclusive merchandise upon arrival / Front Row VIP AREA presented by Three Sheets Brewing / access to all GA areas as well as the private VIP area.</i><br>\t<br>\n<b>Exclusive Suite 19+ for 12 people:</b> <i>Includes Finger food, alcohol, and soft drinks, along with stage front access.</i></p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
