      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "HEARTBROKEN: Tom Petty & The Heartbreakers"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "\n<p> HEARTBROKEN:  A Tom Petty Experience is a tribute act that faithfully recreates the iconic sound of Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers. Immerse yourself in a journey through hours of hits,  including 'Free Fallin', 'I Won't Back Down', 'American Girl', 'Refugee Learning to Fly' and many more.</p>\n\n<p>With unparalleled accuracy, the band captures the essence of Tom Petty's music, ensuring an unforgettable experience for fans old and new. With a combined total of 150 years of stage, studio, and teaching roles, the members bring a wealth of experience to every performance.</p>\n\n<p>With the band members having performed on some of the biggest stages across the country,  Heartbroken delivers a tribute that pays homage to the legendary artist and his timeless music. Get ready to be transported into the heart of Tom Petty's soundscape!</p>\n\n<p>A show that is sure to please any TOM PETTY Fan!</p>\n\n<p>HEARTBROKEN is a MUST SEE SHOW!</p>\n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/zz1tTrIkxpU?si=IyzL_VTtQlTXLsV3' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\n</style>"
      }
