    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "In Support of Make-A-Wish Canada: Crystal Jukebox"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b>The Best of Styx & Foreigner</b></p>\n\n<p>This high energy act will take you back to the arena rock, performing hit after hit from a catalogue of some of the most iconic and successful songs ever written.  Not only are the songs performed with note for note precession and in the original recorded keys, but costume changes and visuals make attending a Crystal Jukebox performance even more enjoyable. Audience members can't stop themselves from singing along. So much FUN!!</p>\n\n<p>In proud support of Make-A-Wish Canada</p>\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
