  {
    "@id": "https://ticketpro.ca/event/1669665826",
    "@type": [
      "http://schema.org/Event"
    ],
    "http://schema.org/startDate": [
      {
        "@type": "http://schema.org/Date",
        "@value": "2026-05-04T19:30:00-06:00"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/location": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ticketpro.ca/place/7847311"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/image": [
      {
        "@id": "https://tprowest.ticketpro.ca/api/v1/resources/1669664863.jpeg?version=1"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/offers": [
      {
        "@id": "_:g1235120"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww2.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7225"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww2.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7225"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Louisiana Hayride Farewell Show"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "\n<p>After 16 years of touring across western Canada,<b>the time has come for the Louisiana Hayride Show to say goodbye.</b> </p> \n\n<p>Join original Louisiana Hayride Show members Andrea Anderson, William Brookfield, Gil and Lori Risling, along with longtime members Vic de Sousa, Derek Pulliam, Terry Hoknes and Jordan Perry as they celebrate 16 years of bringing this show to you! <b>Come out one last time to join in the celebration and say goodbye.</b></p>\n\n<p>This is your last chance to take a trip down memory lane with this unique and incredibly entertaining musical celebration. </p>\n\n<p>The Louisiana Hayride Show, with amazing world class tribute artists and live band will bring you <b>back in time to when songs were meaningful, the words were understood and the sound was pleasant.</b></p>\n\n<p>Legendary stars will come to life before your eyes! <b>You'll think you're at their concert when you see Patsy Cline, Loretta Lynn,  Roy Orbison, Willie Nelson, Shania Twain, Crystal Gayle, Elvis Presley and Buddy Holly step on stage to sing their big hits, all in one incredible show!</b></p>\n\n<p>In addition to these amazing tribute artists and their songs, you'll also hear classics by <b>Johnny Cash,  Jerry Lee Lewis, Roger Miller and more!</b></p>\n\n<p>You'll hear timeless songs you can sing along to such as <b>Crazy,  Coalminer's Daughter, Ring of Fire,  Honey I'm Home,  King of the Road, Great Balls of Fire, Hound Dog, That'll Be the Day, Pretty Woman, On the Road Again and many more!</b></p>\n\n<p>This is the Louisiana Hayride's last show but it <b>will feature some exciting 'firsts' you don't want to miss! There will be new and fun material to keep you surprised and totally entertained from start to finish.</b></p>\n\n<p>Don't miss the opportunity to see this amazing show one last time.</p>\n\n<p><b>BC and SK shows sold out quickly so tell your friends and family and get your tickets now before the Alberta shows sell out. For more information and complete tour schedule, go to <a href='https://www.hayrideshow.com' target='_blank'>www.hayrideshow.com</a></b></p>\n\n"
      }
    ],
