    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Major Talent Inc. presents Hotel California"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>HOTEL CALIFORNIA, the original Eagles tribute is here at the Georgian Theatre Saturday May 9 and you will want to be here too.  </p>\n\n<p>For almost three decades, HOTEL CALIFORNIA has been re-creating the legendary sound of THE EAGLES, and thrilling audiences all over the world. The band set the bar in 1986 and they've remained the industry leading substitute for The Eagles ever since, playing to huge outdoor and arena audiences, sharing bills with some of rock's legends, and going places no tribute band has gone before.</p>\n\n<p>You can count on incredible lead vocal similarity, intensely accurate instrumental work, soaring harmonies, and a top flight live performance.</p>\n\n<p>HOTEL CALIFORNIA's show has evolved into a masterful celebration of The Eagles' music, as one of the most game-changing song catalogs in the history of rock n' roll is performed to perfection.</p>\n\n<p>If you love The Eagles - you've just found the next-best thing.</p>\n\n\n\n"
      }
    ],
