      {
        "@value": "<p>The <b>Round 4</b> Playoff Schedule against the <b>Toronto Patriots</b>:</p>\n\n<p><b>Game 2</b> | Sunday, April 19, 2026 at 7:00 p.m.<br>\n<b>Game 4</b> | Friday, April 24, 2026 at 7:30 p.m.<br>\n<b>Game 6</b> <i>(if necessary)</i> | Monday, April 27, 2026 at 7:00 p.m. </p>\n\n<p>#Can'tOutrunTheStorm🌪️</p>\n\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>"
