    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Simcoe Contemporary Dancers presents Celebration of Dance"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>SCD is thrilled to announce that we are hosting the 22nd Annual Celebration of Dance!</p>\n\n<p>Celebration of Dance is a special fundraising event where SCD invites dancers from all over Simcoe County to come together to raise money for a local charity. This event is an amazing opportunity to see a variety of dance styles, unique choreography, and support a worthy cause.</p>\n\n<p>Since the inception of Celebration of Dance, the event has raised over $45,000 for charities!</p>\n\n<p>This year we will be hosting Celebration of Dance in support of <a href='https://www.glowingheartscharity.org/' target='_blank'>Glowing Hearts Charity</a> - an organization whose focus is to disrupt the cycle of poverty by providing programs that reduce barriers and support the mental health, growth, and development of school-age children and youth in Simcoe County.</p>\n\n<p><a href='https://www.scdancers.com/event/22nd-annual-celebration-of-dance/' target='_blank'>https://www.scdancers.com/event/22nd-annual-celebration-of-dance</a></p>\n\n<style>.location-page-temp {display: none!important;}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
