    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Stageworks Academy Presents Your BIG Show - Alice in Wonderland / Wizard of Oz"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b>Alice in Wonderland </b><br>\nLadies and gentlemen, boys and girls, welcome to a world where nothing is quite as it seems! Tonight, Stageworks proudly invites you to tumble down the rabbit hole into the curious and colorful adventure of Alice in Wonderland — a magical journey filled with talking rabbits, mischievous cats, mad tea parties, and a Queen who is always ready to shout, 'Off with their heads!' As young Alice discovers, Wonderland is a place where imagination runs wild, courage is tested, and the impossible becomes possible. So sit back, open your hearts, and prepare to believe in six impossible things before intermission as our talented performers bring this whimsical classic to life!</p>\n\n<p><b>Wizard of OZ</b><br>\nLadies and gentlemen, boys and girls, welcome to a journey beyond the rainbow! Tonight, we invite you to step into a world of courage, heart, and a little bit of magic as we present our dramatic adaptation of The Wizard of Oz. When a Kansas farm girl named Dorothy is swept away by a swirling storm, she finds herself in the dazzling Land of Oz, joined by a brain-seeking Scarecrow, a heart-longing Tin Man, and a courage-craving Lion. Together, they travel the Yellow Brick Road toward a mysterious wizard, discovering along the way that the very things they seek have been within them all along. So click your heels, follow the Emerald glow, and prepare to be reminded that there truly is no place like home. </p>\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
      }
