    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Stageworks Academy Presents Your BIG Show - Guys & Dolls"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Ladies and gentlemen, welcome to a dazzling trip to the streets of 1950s New York City! Tonight, we're rolling the dice and raising the curtain on Guys and Dolls Jr., where high-stakes gamblers, big-hearted showgirls, and determined missionaries collide in a whirlwind of romance, laughter, and unforgettable music. From Times Square to Havana, this toe-tapping adventure reminds us that love can surprise you, luck can change in an instant, and sometimes the biggest gamble of all is following your heart. So grab your fedoras, keep an eye on your wallets, and get ready for a show that's sure to be a sure bet — it's time for Guys and Dolls Jr.! </p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
      }
