    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Stageworks Academy Presents Your BIG Show - We the North"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Ladies and gentlemen, welcome to a celebration of strength, spirit, and sound from the True North! Today's dance showcase, We the North, is inspired by the passion and pride that echoes across our country — a phrase made famous by the Toronto Raptors and embraced by Canadians everywhere. This high-energy production honors iconic Canadian artists and the powerful music that has shaped generations, blending bold choreography with heart, resilience, and unmistakable northern fire. From chart-topping anthems to soulful ballads, our dancers bring to life the rhythm of a nation that stands strong, dreams big, and moves together. Get ready to feel the beat, embrace the pride, and celebrate the incredible talent that makes us proudly say — We the North!</p>\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
      }
