      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Paquette Productions Presents The Legendary Patsy Cline Show"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b>The Legendary Patsy Cline Show starring Amberley Beatty </b> <br>\nPresented by Paquette Productions </p>\n\n<p>When Amberley Beatty steps on to the stage, the spirit, and the very soul of one of the  greatest singers in the history of pop and country music comes to life. From the classic  western style, to the stunning evening gown, complete with the bright red lipstick, she  embodies the sultry sound of the legendary Patsy Cline. </p>\n\n<p>So here begins this magical ride; expect to sing along, laugh, and at times be brought to  tears by this very special performance. From chart busters like I Fall To Pieces, She's  Got You, Crazy and the bone chilling Faded Love, all the hits of the one and only Patsy  Cline are featured in this incredible show. Get ready to go Walking After Midnight with  Amberley Beatty in the legendary Patsy Cline show! </p>\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
