    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww2.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7450"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Tracy Millar: My Roots Are Showing"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "\n<p><center><b>**This is a special standalone event and is independent of our regular concert series**</b></center></p>\n\n<p>Join us at the Max Center for <b>'My Roots Are Showing'</b> — an unforgettable evening of classic country music, dancing, and cabaret-style entertainment featuring the talented <b>Tracy Millar.</b><br><br>\n\nStep into a warm and lively cabaret atmosphere where great music, laughter, and dancing come together for a night filled with energy and nostalgia. This special show celebrates the golden era of country music, featuring beloved hits from the 1960s through the early 1980s — from Ray Price to Crystal Gayle, Charley Pride to Dolly Parton, and everything in between... with a little Tracy Millar magic woven throughout.<br><br>\n\nA seasoned performer and one of Alberta's most respected champions of traditional country music, Tracy Millar has spent more than two decades captivating audiences as a singer, songwriter, bandleader, and recording artist. Her authentic sound, heartfelt delivery, and deep love for classic country shine through every performance, making each show a genuine celebration of the music that defined generations.<br><br>\n\nIf you love true country music, this is a night you won't want to miss. Steel guitar, fiddle, timeless songs, and a dance floor ready for you — what more could you ask for?<br><br>\n\nCome celebrate the songs, the memories, and the spirit of classic country music with friends old and new. Put on your dancing shoes and join us for a night that promises great music, great company, and unforgettable moments.<br><br>\n\n<b>Classic country. Live music. Dancing. Cabaret atmosphere.<br></b>\nAll that's missing is you!</p>\n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/YVeFeQpO3sw?si=XyrMXPB5si0xJVt6' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>\n"
      }
    ],
